{"tid":1554234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[FC教學]旺角7人車起火事件","createTime":"2019-09-09T01:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T04:32:07.000Z","uid":21742,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2df2e565d66406101a3f75cfab4c154d66d26b","tid":1554234,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2365338563542345/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2Fphotos%2Fa.701245323285019%2F2365338563542345%2F&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=5550804d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2365338563542345/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69887534_2365338566875678_3058202850044674048_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmjnrJaH6oBpl4Erhv_pQ755qB2xiDMXocfQH6FXp1oArq9aX-Xws7byFG1G5p7M3M&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=bb6514c9a1a03dbc7fa01a29c4cdffdc&amp;oe=5DC95594\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69887534_2365338566875678_3058202850044674048_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmjnrJaH6oBpl4Erhv_pQ755qB2xiDMXocfQH6FXp1oArq9aX-Xws7byFG1G5p7M3M%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dbb6514c9a1a03dbc7fa01a29c4cdffdc%26oe%3D5DC95594&h=814bb9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一幅相引起無數想像，然後...<br />\n<br />\n左上：疑被縱火（留言多指控警察）<br />\n左下：被縱火焚燒（圖)(留言多指控示威者）<br />\n右上下：消防調查後無可疑，其實是司機自己報警。<br />\n<br />\n任何沒有出處的相片，請網民們冷靜處理，可以嘗試搜索新聞才下判斷，否則就會造成資訊混亂。<br />\n<br />\n「男司機立刻開車門跳落車走避，並報警求助。消防員接報到場，迅速將火救熄，經初步調查後，認為起火原因無可疑，不排除機件故障引致。」-東方日報<br />\n<br />\n「經調查後相信是汽車引擎過熱起火，起火原因沒有可疑。」-香港01<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：<br />\n金水(己del)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2432887886798020?sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F178965725523592%2Fposts%2F2432887886798020%3Fsfns%3Dxmwa&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=a8c2556e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/178965725523592/posts/2432887886798020?sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n幫港出聲(已del)：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498565150232596/posts/2498827916872966?sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498565150232596%2Fposts%2F2498827916872966%3Fsfns%3Dxmwa&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=23b64d99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498565150232596/posts/2498827916872966?sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n東方：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190908/mobile/bkn-20190908195701201-0908_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190908%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190908195701201-0908_00822_001.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=30eefecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190908/mobile/bkn-20190908195701201-0908_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港01:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/372972/旺角花園街七人車過熱-車頭突然起火-消防調查無可疑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F372972%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E8%A1%97%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1-%E8%BB%8A%E9%A0%AD%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=4ccbf153\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/372972/旺角花園街七人車過熱-車頭突然起火-消防調查無可疑</a>"},{"pid":"c7681f2809ad9cafd9d4388986587cbcb4d17b6e","tid":1554234,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"1ed001bac9764dd9f88e955bfca1eeee39ad1758","tid":1554234,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:07.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"1d0a45c86f03ab91b71de027eb681871